      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Offering a superlative 2018 BMW M2 Competition, featuring the high-revving S55 3.0L twin-mono-scroll turbocharged inline-six. This specimen boasts a closed-deck block design and a forged longitudinal crankshaft for maximum torsional rigidity. The power is managed by a precise 6-speed manual transmission and an electronically controlled Active M Differential, ensuring optimal torque vectoring. The suspension geometry remains factory-spec with zero bushing deflection, complemented by the CFRP high-precision strut brace for enhanced front-end turn-in. Meticulously preserved with original paint thickness and no evidence of thermal stress on the braking system. This is a mechanically flawless, turnkey investment for the discerning purist.",
