      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "Presenting an absolute masterpiece of automotive preservation. This vehicle is in breathtaking, showroom-quality condition, appearing exactly as it did the day it was first delivered. The exterior paint retains a deep, mirror-like luster, free from any swirl marks, stone chips, or door dings. Every panel gap is factory-perfect, and the trim remains dark and supple. Inside, the cabin is a time capsule; the premium leather upholstery shows no signs of wear or creasing, and the interior still carries that faint, distinct new-car aroma. It has been strictly garage-kept in a climate-controlled environment and has never seen rain or snow. Mechanically, the car is beyond reproach, featuring a comprehensive service history with every scheduled maintenance item performed ahead of time by certified technicians. From the pristine engine bay to the spotless undercarriage, the attention to detail is evident in every corner. This is not just a used car; it is a meticulously curated specimen for the discerning enthusiast who demands nothing less than perfection.",
